      "description": "The 7RCC Spot Bitcoin and Carbon Credit Futures ETF (BTCK) is an exchange-traded fund that is based on the 7RCC Kaiko Bitcoin Carbon Credit index. The funds investment objective is to reflect the daily changes of the price in bitcoin and carbon credit futures contracts (Carbon Credit Futures), as represented by the 7RCC Vinter Bitcoin Carbon Credit Index (the Index), less expenses from the Funds operations. BTCK was launched on Jun 3, 2026 and is issued by Teucrium.",
